00:08.310 --> 00:10.510
Hey, guys!
Prepare to be blown away.

00:10.540 --> 00:11.740
Is there a hurricave coming?

00:13.340 --> 00:14.710
Time to take emergency measures!

00:16.610 --> 00:18.350
What are you doing?

00:18.380 --> 00:21.520
It took me two hours to give
my hair this windswept look.

00:21.550 --> 00:23.520
I cannot have it ruined by actual wind.

00:25.490 --> 00:27.490
Well, there's no hurricane.

00:27.520 --> 00:30.330
Other than a hurricane of entertainment.

00:31.660 --> 00:33.430
Check out this animated film I made.

00:33.460 --> 00:35.600
Ooh, I love cartoons.

00:35.630 --> 00:38.530
I've watched over 70,000 and kept a log.

00:43.270 --> 00:45.480
How does that tell us which
cartoons you've watched?

00:45.510 --> 00:48.410
It doesn't. I just told you two
interesting things about me.

00:48.450 --> 00:50.480
One, that I've watched a lot of cartoons,

00:50.510 --> 00:52.750
and two, that I've kept a log.

00:53.550 --> 00:55.320
Try to keep up.

00:55.350 --> 00:57.350
You guys are supposed to be prodigies.

01:27.520 --> 01:30.390
So? What did you
guys "think"?

01:37.490 --> 01:40.430
I think I would have
preferred the hurricane.

01:44.270 --> 01:49.570
Well... I liked the font
you used at the end.

01:49.610 --> 01:52.680
Not me. I hated everything.
Including the font.

01:52.710 --> 01:54.340
Helvetica? Really?

01:56.750 --> 02:00.420
Congratulations!
You made me hate cartoons.

02:04.290 --> 02:05.490
So, you didn't like anything about it?

02:07.420 --> 02:10.560
Well, I thought the art was well drawn,

02:10.590 --> 02:15.430
but maybe you could try doing
something more relatable.

02:15.470 --> 02:17.330
Find some inspiration from your life.

02:17.370 --> 02:19.270
They say write what you know.

02:19.300 --> 02:21.500
They also say an apple a
day keeps the doctor away,

02:21.540 --> 02:25.340
but we all know that's not true.

02:25.410 --> 02:28.380
Hey, I told you, I don't need
those counseling sessions!

