03:06.350 --> 03:10.190
<i>♪ Yeah, I am, you are, we are</i>

03:10.220 --> 03:13.620
<i>♪ Exceptional</i> <i>Exceptional</i>

03:13.660 --> 03:16.460
<i>♪ Ooh, ooh, ooh</i>

03:16.490 --> 03:17.590
<i>♪ Ooh, ooh</i>

03:17.630 --> 03:18.630
Whoo!

